Steps for the Practical

Steps to add music.mp3 file
1.	Go to Project → app → src → main → res
2.	Right-click on res
3.	Click New → Android Resource Directory
4.	Set: Resource type: raw
5.	Click OK
6.	Now copy the music file and paste it in the raw.
Install APK Using USB Cable (Android Studio)
 Step 1: Enable Developer Options
1.	Open Settings → About phone
2.	Tap Build number 7 times
3.	You’ll see: “You are now a developer”
 Step 2: Enable USB Debugging
1.	Go to Settings → Developer options
2.	Turn ON USB debugging
3.	Tap OK when prompted
 Step 3: Connect Phone to PC
•	Use a USB cable
•	Select File Transfer (MTP) on phone if asked
Step 4: Install APK from Android Studio
1.	Open your project in Android Studio
2.	Click Run 
3.	Select your connected device
4.	APK will be installed automatically on your phone
